interndetails.name: Jayandra Thapa
interndetails.description: An intern under the guidance of mentor Krishna Guragai, has successfully completed several significant projects during the internship period. These include developing a responsive personal portfolio, a note-taking app, TextUtils App, and a tech website. Jayandra has recently been assigned to the Gurkha Intern Management Application project, where he collaborates effectively with the team to optimize intern administration and communication within the company. His dedication and skills have contributed significantly to the successful execution of these projects.
